_sText:
Ported from CS:GO specially for centralka.ru

Original map: 79330


Jailbreak map set inside and outside a mountain cavern with multiple advantages and disadvantages for both Prisoners and Guards. Be careful where you tread!

Features:

  • 56 T Spawn
  • 24 CT Spawns
  • Cell Area
  • Gun Room
  • 2 Medics
  • Pool
  • Disco (Hidden)

Map Games Include:

  • Colours
  • Skipping (Fully automated)
  • Climb (Including Hard Mode via Lava Button)
  • Race
  • Maze
  • Tower Jump
  • Minefield
  • Bunny Hop
  • Soccer with working ball
  • Four Corners

Plenty of secrets!
